-Who did? -The guy that robbed the bank. Duh.

1188
01:15:07,17 --> 01:15:08,88
儿子，别骂人
Son, be respectful.

1189
01:15:08,96 --> 01:15:11,72
好吧，他是头头吗？
Okay, Brooklyn. But it... Was he the one in charge?

1190
01:15:11,80 --> 01:15:13,09
好
-Uh-huh. -Okay.

1191
01:15:13,18 --> 01:15:15,80
你不记得别的事？
And you don't remember anything else?

1192
01:15:15,97 --> 01:15:17,60
他很高
He was kind of tall.

1193
01:15:18,31 --> 01:15:19,52
戴了面罩
He had a mask.

1194
01:15:19,56 --> 01:15:23,52
布莱恩，你认得出他吗？
Brian, you think you can recognize him in any of these pictures?

1195
01:15:24,52 --> 01:15:26,82
慢慢来，仔细看
Take your time. Have a good look.

1196
01:15:27,36 --> 01:15:30,03
仔细看这些照片
Let's keep that over there. Just take a look.

1197
01:15:36,58 --> 01:15:39,79
-他们戴了面罩看起来都一样 -没错
-With the mask, they look all the same. -It's true.

1198
01:15:41,54 --> 01:15:44,50
戴了面罩看起来都一样
With the mask, they all look the same. That's right, Brian.

1199
01:15:44,58 --> 01:15:47,92
抢劫杂货店未遂
Attempted robbery. Liquor store.

1200
01:15:48,21 --> 01:15:51,59
抢银行算是很大的进步
Well, this was a real step up for a small-timer like you, huh?

1201
01:15:52,38 --> 01:15:54,22
你真有一套，帕罗
I got to hand it to you, Pablo.

1202
01:15:54,26 --> 01:15:57,85
我叫保罗，不是帕罗
First of all, it's Paul. Not Pablo, okay?

1203
01:15:58,06 --> 01:15:59,68
对不起
Excuse me.

1204
01:16:00,31 --> 01:16:02,48
-吃口香糖吗？ -不要
-You want some gum? -No.

1205
01:16:02,94 --> 01:16:04,56
而且不是我干的
And second, I didn't do it, all right?

1206
01:16:04,65 --> 01:16:07,19
我年轻的时候误入歧途
What? I made a few mistakes when I was a kid.

1207
01:16:07,27 --> 01:16:10,57
我的朋友抢劫我刚好也在
I was out with some friends and they held up a liquor store.

1208
01:16:11,65 --> 01:16:13,57
我该怎么办？
What was I supposed to do?

1209
01:16:15,28 --> 01:16:17,41
你是不知民间疾苦的花花大少？
Where'd you grow up, you Wassa Wassa, Park Avenue?

1210
01:16:17,49 --> 01:16:20,04
-花什么？ -花花大少
-What's that? Wassa what? What'd you say? -Wassa Wassa.

1211
01:16:21,37 --> 01:16:23,62
我看你也不像
You know, a person that don't come to your neighborhood.

1212
01:16:23,71 --> 01:16:26,00
监狱西班牙话怎么说？
How do you say "Rikers Island" in Spanish?

1213
01:16:26,08 --> 01:16:27,84
这两个呢？
What about these two?

1214
01:16:28,00 --> 01:16:29,63
有印象吗？
That ring a bell?

1215
01:16:29,71 --> 01:16:31,92
这两个？没有
These two? No.

1216
01:16:31,96 --> 01:16:33,26
-完全没有？ -没有
-Nothing? -Nothing.

1217
01:16:33,30 --> 01:16:34,76
你不觉得他们可疑吗？
Don't they look suspicious to you?

1218
01:16:34,80 --> 01:16:38,26
你不想知道他们是谁？
I mean, I would think that you would want to know who they are.

1219
01:16:38,55 --> 01:16:39,60
不想
No.

1220
01:16:39,64 --> 01:16:41,35
-谢谢你的合作 -谢谢
-Well, thank you very much. -Thank you.

1221
01:16:41,43 --> 01:16:44,14
你对钻石知道多少？
Hey, just out of curiosity do you know anything about diamonds?

1222
01:16:44,23 --> 01:16:46,27
不少，你需要什么？
A bit. What do you need?

1223
01:16:46,35 --> 01:16:48,65
一只钻戒要多少钱？
What do you think a guy like me should pay for a diamond ring?

1224
01:16:48,73 --> 01:16:50,69
这要看是几克拉
Depends. How many carats?

1225
01:16:50,77 --> 01:16:52,78
找我侄子
If you'd like, I could give you my nephew's number.

1226
01:16:52,82 --> 01:16:54,24
-好 -他会给你打折
-Okay. -You'll get a very good deal.

1227
01:16:54,32 --> 01:16:56,28
底下是什么？
What do you have on underneath?

1228
01:16:56,49 --> 01:16:58,70
-什么？ -你的衣服底下穿什么？
-Excuse me? -Underneath your painter's coat?

1229
01:16:58,78 --> 01:17:00,95
-你底下穿什么？ -小可爱
-What do you have on underneath? -Clothing.

1230
01:17:01,03 --> 01:17:03,16
让我们看
Could you show us, please?

1231
01:17:07,42 --> 01:17:09,46
你和另一个女人
You see, there's just you and one other woman

1232
01:17:09,50 --> 01:17:12,13
符合女嫌犯特征
that fit the physical description of the female suspect.

1233
01:17:12,17 --> 01:17:13,96
什么特征？
What's that?

1234
01:17:14,84 --> 01:17:18,14
身高、年龄还有…
It's your height, your age, and your...

1235
01:17:19,01 --> 01:17:20,39
罩杯大小
Your cup size.

1236
01:17:20,47 --> 01:17:23,93
我违反了第34条DD条款吗？
So, I violated Section 34 double-D?

1237
01:17:24,02 --> 01:17:25,93
是不是这意思？
That's what you're telling me?

1238
01:17:29,56 --> 01:17:32,82
这白痴真以为会有飞机吗？
How dumb do these morons have to be to think they're gonna get a plane?

1239
01:17:32,86 --> 01:17:34,03
他不是白痴
This guy's no moron.

1240
01:17:34,11 --> 01:17:36,82
不只是他，每一个挟持人质者
I don't just mean him. Any hostage taker.

1241
01:17:38,24 --> 01:17:40,87
慕尼黑奥运那些恐怖份子
Those ragheads at the Munich Olympics.

1242
01:17:41,33 --> 01:17:42,95
他们上得了飞机吗？
Who the fuck ever got a plane?

1243
01:17:43,04 --> 01:17:45,66
难道他不知道吗？
Shit, and these days? This guy doesn't know that?

1244
01:17:45,75 --> 01:17:49,46
这里戒备深严，狙击手在屋顶…
The area is flooded with law enforcement right now. Snipers are on rooftops...

1245
01:17:49,54 --> 01:17:50,83
你在干嘛？
What you doing there, Keith?

1246
01:17:50,88 --> 01:17:52,67
他要飞机我就给他飞机
He wants a plane. I'm gonna give him a plane.

1247
01:17:52,71 --> 01:17:55,51
-你不遵守谈判手册？ -我就是觉得不对劲
-What happened to playing it by the book? -That's what's bugging me.

1248
01:17:55,55 --> 01:17:59,89
他们好像也看过谈判手册
It's like the other team read the book, too, and they know exactly what we're gonna do.

1249
01:18:02,89 --> 01:18:06,39
从头到尾都不是我们在拖延时间
This whole time, we're trying to stall him, right?

1250
01:18:06,48 --> 01:18:08,27
而是他们在拖延时间
Wrong. They're the ones that are stalling.

1251
01:18:08,35 --> 01:18:10,77
什么狗屁谜语、阿尔巴尼亚录音
Think about it. The bullshit questions, the Albanian thing...

1252
01:18:10,85 --> 01:18:12,36
这代表什么？
So, you're saying he what?

1253
01:18:12,40 --> 01:18:15,53
他要给我们更多时间，他提出要求和时限
I'm saying that he wants to give us more time. He makes demands.

1254
01:18:16,19 --> 01:18:19,45
我们尽量拖，他就给更多时间
He gives us deadlines. We stall. Then he gives us more time.

1255
01:18:19,53 --> 01:18:20,91
他一点都不急
I don't think he's in a rush.

1256
01:18:20,95 --> 01:18:23,20
-为什么？ -我要去查清楚
-Why? -That's what I'm gonna find out.

1257
01:18:44,43 --> 01:18:46,01
-喂？ -飞机准备好了
-Yeah. -Your plane is ready.

1258
01:18:46,10 --> 01:18:47,22
是吗？
Is that a fact?

1259
01:18:47,31 --> 01:18:49,81
对，不过你要先为我做一件事
That's a fact, but I'm gonna need something from you first.

1260
01:18:49,89 --> 01:18:52,94
我要亲眼看到人质平安无事
I'm gonna need to come in there and make sure the hostages are okay.

1261
01:18:53,02 --> 01:18:54,73
你会在巴士上看到他们
You'll see them when they get on the bus.

1262
01:18:54,82 --> 01:18:58,24
我要确定你没留下任何人
I just need to make sure you're not leaving any bodies behind.

1263
01:19:00,74 --> 01:19:02,45
到前门找我
Meet me at the front door.

1264
01:19:08,54 --> 01:19:11,75
-怎么回事？ -你疯了才会进去
-What the hell just happened? -You got to be crazy to go in there.

1265
01:20:01,84 --> 01:20:03,43
楼下
Down the stairs.

1266
01:20:11,52 --> 01:20:13,56
-口香糖？ -什么？
-Gum? -Excuse me?

1267
01:20:13,64 --> 01:20:16,65
-你要吃口香糖吗？ -不要，谢了
-Would you like some gum? -No, thank you.

1268
01:21:06,03 --> 01:21:07,99
让我把小孩带走
Let me take the kid.

1269
01:21:09,24 --> 01:21:10,78
不行
No.

1270
01:21:11,24 --> 01:21:12,91
还有吗？
Any more?

1271
01:21:13,08 --> 01:21:15,21
有些人不乖乖听话
There are some who misbehaved.

1272
01:21:21,25 --> 01:21:22,88
救我！
Please help me!

1273
01:21:23,76 --> 01:21:25,17
救我们！
Please help us!

1274
01:21:25,26 --> 01:21:27,72
请你救救我们！
Please help us! Please!

1275
01:21:28,39 --> 01:21:30,51
我们一定会救你们出去
We're gonna get you all out of here.

1276
01:21:30,60 --> 01:21:32,35
我保证
I promise you.

1277
01:21:33,10 --> 01:21:34,81
参观结束
Tour is over.

1278
01:21:42,82 --> 01:21:46,24
-我问你一个问题 -没什么好谈的
-Can I ask you a question? -There is nothing to talk about.

1279
01:21:46,86 --> 01:21:48,57
我真的弄到飞机
What were you planning on doing

1280
01:21:48,61 --> 01:21:51,20
你会怎样？
if you actually got the plane and the pilots, huh?

1281
01:21:51,78 --> 01:21:54,58
-什么？ -你从头到尾都不要飞机
-Excuse me? -You don't want a plane. You never did.

1282
01:21:54,62 --> 01:21:57,96
谁听过银行抢匪带人质逃逸？
Who ever heard of bank robbers escaping on a plane with 50 hostages?

1283
01:21:58,00 --> 01:22:01,42
你也看过《热天午后》，你一直在拖延时间
You saw Dog Day Afternoon. You're stalling. Why? I don't know.

1284
01:22:02,29 --> 01:22:04,80
我不知道为什么，怎么？打不开保险库？
What's the matter? You can't get into the safe?

1285
01:22:04,84 --> 01:22:06,47
也许吧
Perhaps.

1286
01:22:07,34 --> 01:22:08,80
你只有两个选择
There's two ways out of this.

1287
01:22:08,84 --> 01:22:12,81
跟我一起走出这道门或是让霹雳小组进行攻坚
The easy way, we walk out the front door together, or the hard boys cut the power,

1288
01:22:12,85 --> 01:22:15,72
丢催泪弹，闯进来火拼一场
hit you with the tear gas, and come in strong through the glass.

1289
01:22:15,81 --> 01:22:18,77
你我都不希望有这种结果
It's your choice. You don't want that. I don't want that.

1290
01:22:18,81 --> 01:22:21,06
他们今晚就想行动
And, you know, they'd like to do it tonight.

1291
01:22:21,15 --> 01:22:23,02
你们有夜视镜
You got night vision?

1292
01:22:23,48 --> 01:22:26,11
-和防毒面罩吗？ -也许有
-You got gas masks? -Maybe.

1293
01:22:27,32 --> 01:22:29,86
-我就快要下令攻坚了 -废话少说
-I'm this close to ordering it. -Let's cut the crap.

1294
01:22:29,95 --> 01:22:32,95
没有死伤或威胁
First, you don't order an assault when no hostages have been killed

1295
01:22:32,99 --> 01:22:34,54
不能下令攻坚
and there's no immediate threat.

1296
01:22:34,62 --> 01:22:37,66
如果真的要火拼一场
Second, if it ends that way, whatever happens,

1297
01:22:37,75 --> 01:22:39,46
你的麻烦就大了
you don't get to be the hero.

1298
01:22:39,50 --> 01:22:41,71
你想唬我，想都别想
You want to bullshit me, try harder.

1299
01:22:42,50 --> 01:22:44,04
走吧
Let's go.

1300
01:22:45,59 --> 01:22:47,09
好
Okay.

1301
01:22:54,26 --> 01:22:57,22
告诉你，我不会有麻烦
I tell you what. My ass is covered, sport.

1302
01:22:57,31 --> 01:22:59,94
你也别想在这儿舒服地享福
But I would not get too comfortable in here if I were you.

1303
01:23:00,02 --> 01:23:02,65
才怪，礼拜三要装第四台了
No? I got the cable guy coming on Wednesday.

1304
01:23:03,31 --> 01:23:05,98
-你何不走出大门？ -我会的
-Why don't you just walk out the door? -I will.

1305
01:23:07,78 --> 01:23:10,90
我准备好就会大摇大摆走出去
I'm gonna walk out of that door when I'm good and ready.

1306
01:23:11,20 --> 01:23:13,20
今天行不行？
Can I get you to do that today?

1307
01:23:14,99 --> 01:23:16,33
不行
I didn't think so.

1308
01:23:16,37 --> 01:23:17,70
你有其它要求吗？
Any other proposals?

1309
01:23:17,75 --> 01:23:20,00
别说“求”这个字
Oh, please. Do not say "proposals."

1310
01:23:20,04 --> 01:23:22,83
我女友要我跟她求婚
My girlfriend, she wants a proposal from me.

1311
01:23:22,88 --> 01:23:26,59
-你觉得太年轻不想安定下来？ -不是太年轻，是太穷了
-You think you're too young to get married? -No, I'm not too young. Too broke.

1312
01:23:26,67 --> 01:23:28,88
也许我也该抢银行
Maybe I should rob a bank.

1313
01:23:29,97 --> 01:23:31,93
你们真心相爱吗？
You love each other?

1314
01:23:32,22 --> 01:23:34,01
当然了
Yeah. Yeah, we do.

1315
01:23:34,18 --> 01:23:36,35
那钱就不是问题
Then money shouldn't really matter.

1316
01:23:36,89 --> 01:23:38,89
多谢开导，银行抢匪
Thank you, bank robber.

1317
01:23:38,93 --> 01:23:42,19
我只是说金钱买不到真爱
I'm just saying money can't buy love.

1318
01:23:43,94 --> 01:23:46,61
我真心地谢谢你
Thank you very much. I'm ...

1319
01:23:48,03 --> 01:23:50,28
我今天学到好多
I'm learning so much today, you know?

1320
01:23:51,03 --> 01:23:53,86
咱们不如一起去对街的酒吧
Look, why don't we go across the street to the Killarney Rose, huh?

1321
01:23:53,91 --> 01:23:55,78
忘了这件事
Forget about this dangerous hostage situation.

1322
01:23:55,87 --> 01:23:58,37
-我请你喝酒 -谢了，警探
-I'll buy you a beer. My treat. -Thanks, Detective,

1323
01:23:58,45 --> 01:24:01,58
我还不想坐牢
but I'm trying to stay away from bars, if you know what I mean.

1324
01:24:01,66 --> 01:24:05,17
你再好好考虑一下
Well, if you change your mind there's still a standing offer, all right?

1325
01:24:10,92 --> 01:24:13,13
你想被关进监牢
Cellblock or the graveyard?

1326
01:24:13,22 --> 01:24:15,01
还是埋在坟墓？
Prison whites or a toe tag?

1327
01:24:15,09 --> 01:24:18,56
-最好赶快决定，分秒必争 -嘿！
-Make up your mind. Tick tock, tick tock. -Hey! Hey!

1328
01:24:19,47 --> 01:24:21,39
你闹够了吗？
We done?

1329
01:24:23,52 --> 01:24:25,65
你做得太过份了
You just crossed the fucking line!

1330
01:24:27,44 --> 01:24:29,61
巴士，停在外面
Buses, Kojak, parked outside.

1331
01:24:30,15 --> 01:24:32,32
你以为我在虚张声势？
You think I'm bluffing?

1332
01:24:32,95 --> 01:24:35,32
你就等着瞧吧
You roll the dice and see what happens.

1333
01:24:44,29 --> 01:24:46,29
举起盾牌
All right. Now get the bunker up.

1334
01:24:46,38 --> 01:24:48,42
-怎么样？ -我让他完全掌控大局
-So, what's up? -Got him right where I want him.

1335
01:24:48,46 --> 01:24:49,63
怎么说？
Yeah? Where's that?

1336
01:24:49,71 --> 01:24:53,17
我让他把我吃得死死的
Right behind me with my pants around my ankles, but it's a start.

1337
01:24:53,26 --> 01:24:54,80
天啊
Jesus Christ.

1338
01:25:09,31 --> 01:25:10,77
-搞什么？ -还要多久？
-What the fuck, man? -How long?

1339
01:25:10,86 --> 01:25:12,15
-他把你撂倒了 -两小时
-He got the drop on you! -Two.

1340
01:25:12,23 --> 01:25:13,78
-多久？ -他看到你的脸怎么办？
-How long? -What if he saw your face?

1341
01:25:13,86 --> 01:25:15,40
-两小时 -如果我当时没枪怎么办？
-Two. -What if I didn't have my gun?

1342
01:25:15,49 --> 01:25:17,07
两、三小时
Two, maybe three hours.

1343
01:25:17,16 --> 01:25:20,45
你让那警察太接近了
You know, you're letting this cop get too fucking close.

1344
01:25:23,41 --> 01:25:24,62
怎么回事？
What happened?

1345
01:25:24,66 --> 01:25:26,67
我给他很多藉口把我一枪轰掉
I gave him every excuse to blow my brains out.

1346
01:25:26,75 --> 01:25:27,75
对
Yeah.

1347
01:25:27,83 --> 01:25:30,96
他却没下手，为什么？他不会杀人
He doesn't bite. Why? He ain't the type.

1348
01:25:31,05 --> 01:25:33,55
让我们好好想想这一点
Let's just step back and think about this for a second.

1349
01:25:33,63 --> 01:25:37,13
他一切都计划周详，录音带、摄影机、工作服
We know that they planned this whole thing. The tape, the cameras, the costumes.

1350
01:25:37,22 --> 01:25:39,55
计划并不包括飞机
There was a game plan, but it never included airplanes.

1351
01:25:39,64 --> 01:25:42,31
他另有目的，但是不会伤人
He's up to something but it ain't violence.

1352
01:25:46,31 --> 01:25:48,85
-我在听 -收讯品质如何？
-I'm listening. -How's the reception?

1353
01:25:49,27 --> 01:25:51,69
-什么？ -车上的摄影机
-Excuse me? -The camera on the truck.

1354
01:25:52,11 --> 01:25:54,74
给二楼窗口来个特写镜头
Give me a close-up on the second-floor window.

1355
01:25:55,44 --> 01:25:57,36
-小骆？ -马上好
-Rourke? -I'm on it, I'm on it.

1356
01:26:08,92 --> 01:26:11,42
不要！
No, no, no, no, no, no! Fuck!

1357
01:26:11,50 --> 01:26:13,05
我靠
Oh, shit.

1358
01:26:16,42 --> 01:26:19,22
基斯！
Keith! Keith! Keith!

1359
01:26:25,56 --> 01:26:27,89
你在干什么？
What are you doing? What the fuck are you doing?

1360
01:26:27,98 --> 01:26:30,06
这不是很明显吗？
You mean beyond the obvious?

1361
01:26:30,23 --> 01:26:32,73
你并不是在抢银行
That's what I mean. Come on, this ain't no bank robbery!

1362
01:26:32,77 --> 01:26:35,69
这是你的错，我叫你准备巴士
This is your fault. I told you to get the buses.

1363
01:26:35,73 --> 01:26:39,20
去你的，我没有杀任何人
Fuck you! I didn't kill anybody.

1364
01:26:41,28 --> 01:26:43,99
我还有五十个人质，你敢再惹我
I got 50 more people in here. You fuck with me again,

1365
01:26:44,08 --> 01:26:46,20
这两天会很漫长
I'll give you two of the longest days of your life.

1366
01:26:46,29 --> 01:26:50,58
告诉我你到底要什么，我一定替你办到
All right, look, just tell me what it is you really want and I'll get it for you.

1367
01:26:50,67 --> 01:26:53,50
-我保证 -我说过，两辆巴士、一架飞机
-I promise. -I've told you. Two buses, a plane.

1368
01:26:53,59 --> 01:26:56,30
还有洋基球场的贵宾包厢票
Right, right. And box seats behind home plate at Yankee Stadium.

1369
01:26:56,38 --> 01:26:58,63
别再唬弄我
Come on, don't bullshit a bullshitter.

1370
01:26:59,30 --> 01:27:01,76
你的计划周详
You planned every inch of this thing right from the start.

1371
01:27:01,80 --> 01:27:05,60
我们都被你牵着鼻子走，不过我不随你起舞了
You got everybody marching to your beat, including me, and I'm through buying it.

1372
01:27:08,77 --> 01:27:10,98
你太聪明，不该当警察
You're too damn smart to be a cop.

1373
01:27:11,06 --> 01:27:12,81
给我滚出去
Now get the fuck out of here.

1374
01:27:12,90 --> 01:27:14,77
你要杀我吗？
What? You going to shoot me?

1375
01:27:15,44 --> 01:27:16,98
下手呀，你都杀了人了
Do it. Shit, you got nothing to lose.

1376
01:27:17,07 --> 01:27:19,36
没什么好损失的，开枪呀
I damn sure ain't got nothing to lose, so shoot me.

1377
01:27:19,78 --> 01:27:21,24
下手呀
Do it.

1378
01:27:21,28 --> 01:27:23,32
-杀了我 -去你的
-Shoot me. -Fuck you.

1379
01:27:24,03 --> 01:27:26,54
叫他们派个正常人来
Tell them to send someone sane over here.

1380
01:27:55,48 --> 01:27:56,94
出了大问题
We got a big problem.

1381
01:27:57,02 --> 01:27:59,11
今天你衰毙了
Hey, Detective, this ain't your day.

1382
01:28:05,91 --> 01:28:07,66
你好，队长
How you doing, Captain?

1383
01:28:09,45 --> 01:28:11,50
我知道你信任我
Look, I know you put your trust in me and I just...

1384
01:28:11,58 --> 01:28:14,37
你是个好警察
Well, you're a good cop. Frazier, I need more like you.

1385
01:28:14,46 --> 01:28:16,79
不过这次我不能被你拖下水
But if you're going down on this one, I can't go with you.

1386
