You got to understand this, though, sir...

1387
01:28:18,50 --> 01:28:20,71
我的问题是
No, no, no. Let me just tell you what my problem is, okay?

1388
01:28:20,80 --> 01:28:22,76
我上床睡觉，一切OK
I go to bed, everything's hunky-dory.

1389
01:28:22,84 --> 01:28:25,22
到了半夜就死了一个人质
I get a call at 3:15, and there's what? A dead hostage.

1390
01:28:25,30 --> 01:28:28,10
-对，不过我能阻止他… -事情结束了
-Right, right, right. But I can end this... -It is ended.

1391
01:28:28,51 --> 01:28:30,47
我也别无选择
See, you think I got options.

1392
01:28:30,52 --> 01:28:32,81
这是上头的命令
I got to answer to the Chief of D's .

1393
01:28:32,89 --> 01:28:35,35
戴队长负责指挥攻坚行动
Darius is calling the shots on this. That's it.

1394
01:28:52,45 --> 01:28:54,25
嘿，警官
Hey, Sarge.

1395
01:28:54,54 --> 01:28:56,67
-他怎么说？ -就这样
-What'd he say? -That's it.

1396
01:28:57,92 --> 01:28:59,50
可恶
Shit.

1397
01:29:00,59 --> 01:29:03,22
-这是一场恶梦 -我知道
-It's a tactical nightmare. -I know.

1398
01:29:03,30 --> 01:29:06,34
这是唯一的入口
Well, first, this is the only way in.

1399
01:29:06,43 --> 01:29:08,68
然后要摸黑到楼上
Then we got to make it up the stairs blind.

1400
01:29:08,76 --> 01:29:11,06
一上去立刻成为标靶
Once we get up there, we're right out in the open.

1401
01:29:11,14 --> 01:29:15,14
