-Keep moving. -To the right.

1408
01:29:51,56 --> 01:29:53,06
注意情况
Watch the hands, watch the hands.

1409
01:29:53,10 --> 01:29:55,60
人质一定会死伤惨重
And let's not forget the possibility of hostages being killed.

1410
01:29:55,64 --> 01:29:57,48
把枪放下！
Right now! Put the gun down!

1411
01:29:57,56 --> 01:30:00,40
退后！不然我就开枪
Back off or I shoot! I said back off!

1412
01:30:00,44 --> 01:30:03,82
唯一的机会是让抢匪落单
Well, our best hope is to separate them from the hostages.

1413
01:30:03,90 --> 01:30:06,65
在楼上把他们除掉
If we can get two or three upstairs and take them out?

1414
01:30:06,74 --> 01:30:08,49
射死他们？
Kill them?

1415
01:30:16,12 --> 01:30:17,87
对方有枪！
Gun! Gun! Gun!

1416
01:30:27,01 --> 01:30:28,47
对方不只四个怎么办？
What if there's more than four?

1417
01:30:28,55 --> 01:30:33,26
穿工作服的人都可能是嫌犯
Yeah, well, that's what's so nuts about it. Anybody in a painter's suit could be a perp.

1418
01:30:33,43 --> 01:30:36,68
也许我们也该穿工作服
Maybe we should dress our guys up like a bunch of painters.

1419
01:30:37,56 --> 01:30:41,48
