1421
01:30:45,11 --> 01:30:47,11
那就用橡胶子弹吧
Rubber bullets it is, baby.

1422
01:30:51,66 --> 01:30:53,66
这件事最后死伤惨重
If this goes down wrong,

1423
01:30:54,41 --> 01:30:57,62
责任都会推到你身上
they're going to dump this whole mess in your lap, you know?

1424
01:30:57,70 --> 01:30:59,50
