Everybody's getting theirs. I'm gonna get mine.

1433
01:31:24,82 --> 01:31:26,57
我会在外面
I'll be outside.

1434
01:31:32,20 --> 01:31:33,78
太扯了，太扯了
What a day, what a day.

1435
