So I bust up the fight,

1443
01:31:59,73 --> 01:32:03,44
一转头这小子就拿枪指住我
I turn around and this kid is pointing a .22 at my chest.

1444
01:32:03,52 --> 01:32:07,57
-那小子是什么人？ -一个非裔美国人
-Is that right? Now, which kid was this? -Another kid, an African-American.

1445
01:32:07,65 --> 01:32:09,19
-非裔美国人 -对
-An African-American, right? -Yeah.

1446
01:32:09,28 --> 01:32:10,86
他突然冒出来
Came out of nowhere. I didn't see him.

1447
01:32:10,90 --> 01:32:12,03
后来怎样？
So, what'd you do?

1448
01:32:12,11 --> 01:32:14,28
我告诉你
What did I do then? I'll tell you what I did then.

1449
01:32:14,36 --> 01:32:17,49
我胸口中了一枪
I got shot in the fucking chest. That's what I did then.

1450
01:32:17,70 --> 01:32:20,00
恕我直言哦，警探
Yeah, so you'll pardon my euphemisms, Detective,

1451
01:32:20,08 --> 01:32:23,67
我宁愿种族歧视也不想死
but I would rather wind up an old bigot than a handsome young corpse.

1452
01:32:23,75 --> 01:32:25,38
我没别的意思
Now, no offense, Detective,

1453
01:32:25,42 --> 01:32:27,92
我只是不想让警察被坏人杀死
but I'm just trying to keep them away from us.

1454
01:32:27,96 --> 01:32:31,22
咱们把人质安全救出来吧
Now, what do you say we just get these people safely out of the bank?

1455
01:32:31,26 --> 01:32:32,38
说的好
I hear that.

1456
01:32:32,47 --> 01:32:35,59
我下次说话会小心点
And I'll try and watch what I say in the future.

1457
01:32:35,68 --> 01:32:37,72
谁晓得谁会在听
You never know who's listening.

1458
01:32:52,11 --> 01:32:53,65
你在干嘛？
What are you doing?

1459
01:32:53,74 --> 01:32:55,28
可恶
Jesus. Shit.

1460
01:32:55,61 --> 01:32:57,57
他们在窃听我们
They bugged us.

1461
01:32:57,74 --> 01:32:59,70
他们在窃听我们
They bugged us.

