我们说什么他们都听到
They heard everything we said in the M.C.C.

1468
01:33:13,92 --> 01:33:16,01
-什么？ -撤退！撤退！
-What? -Stand down! Stand down!

1469
01:33:16,09 --> 01:33:19,47
