-On the ground! -Put your hands on your fucking heads!

1497
01:35:31,44 --> 01:35:32,98
别动！
Do not move!

1498
01:35:33,06 --> 01:35:36,19
-趴下来，手放头上！ -帮他们戴上手铐！走吧！
-Get down, put your hands on your head! -Put the cuffs on them! Let's go!

1499
